DB["Apply a Mystic Enchant Scroll at the Mystic Enchanting Altar!"]="Mystic Enchants are the key to acquiring power and succeeding against Azeroth's most powerful foes.\n\nWhether your foe be Demon, pink-haired Gnome, Alliance, or even Horde, the key to victory is acquiring powerful Mystic Enchants to compliment your fighting style and applying them to your character.\n\nYou will find Mystic Enchanting supplies in your mailbox. Summon your Volatile Mystic Altar and use it once placed. Obtain an Untarnished Mystic Scroll and reforge it to receive a Mystic Scroll with an enchant you want to use. If you get an enchant you don't want, you can reforge that enchant repeatedly until you get something you do want. Then you can activate it, and select the Enchantment slot to put it in to increase your character's power!\n\nReforging a Mystic Scroll can be done an infinite number of times, provided you have the Mystic Runes required to reforge them, but extracting the enchant will always DESTROY the scroll You earn extracts by reforging scrolls and leveling up your mystic enchanting."
DB["Apply an enchant to every open active enchant slot."]="Appliquez un enchantement à chaque emplacement d’enchantement actif ouvert."
