DB["Bloodforge a piece of gear"]="You can convert PvE gear or Soulbound PvP gear to Bloodforged Gear using the Bloody Jar.\n\nPurchase a Bloody Jar from Nozdormu. Use the Bloody Jar to convert any item into a Bloodforged item.\n\nBLOODFORGING AN ITEM CAN NOT BE REVERSED. You should only Bloodforge items that are not core to your PvE set or items you wish to convert into PvP items.\n\nBloodforging Soulbound Honor and Arena gear will reduce their stats, but make them tradable. You should only Bloodforge Soulbound PvP gear if you want to trade it.\n\nMystic Enchants, Random Affixes, Gems and Item Enchants are lost when Bloodforging an item."
