DB["Buy Bloodforged Gear from the Auction House."]="You can buy and sell Bloodforged Gear on the Auction House.\n\nYou can use the Auction House to put together a beginner set of PvP gear, fill in missing pieces or find upgrades for your current set of PvP gear. \n\nSoulbound Honor and Arena Gear cannot be bought on the Auction house, and must be earned in game.\n\nSearch the Auction House for any piece of Bloodforged Gear, or add \"PvP\" to your search to find Bloodforged items, then buyout a piece of Bloodforged gear!"
DB["Buy a Vanity Weapon from the Auction House"]="Vanity items allow you to customize the visual appearance of your character to create your unique look and tailor your character to your class fantasy. Ascension offers a huge number of Vanity items to pick from so you can truly stand apart from other Heroes. \n\nYou can find a huge selection of Vanity Items on the Auction House!\n\nOpen the Auction House. Click the Rarity Dropdown and select Vanity. Then hit Search!\n\nYou can Ctrl + Left Click an item to preview its appearance. You can also sort by Current Bid to find the cheapest Vanity items available!\n\nFind and Buyout any Vanity item on the Auction House."
