DB["Complete any Battleground!"]="You can queue for a Battleground from anywhere while you are in No-Risk.\n\nHit H, Click the Battlegrounds Tab and then click Join Battle. \n\nYou will see a faction emblem icon on your minimap indicating you have successfully queue'd for the battleground. Once a Battleground is available, you will receive a pop up that will allow you to the Enter the Battle!\n\nComplete any Battleground. You will still earn Honor and quest completion even if you lose! \n\nIf you find yourself struggling in Battlegrounds ensure you are wearing full PvP Gear, you are fully enchanted with Mystic Enchants that compliment your build. Many players in Battlegrounds have builds specific to PvP. You can optimize your talents for PvP or load a featured PvP Build if you are on Free Pick."
DB["Complete any Call Board Daily Quest."]="Terminez n’importe quelle quête quotidienne du Call Board."
DB["Complete any Heroic Dungeon"]="Open the Dungeon Finder and queue for a Random Heroic Dungeon or pick any of the available Heroic Dungeons under Specific Dungeons.\n\nHeroic Dungeons are more challenging than Normal Dungeons. It is highly recommended that you have full PvE Power before attempting to conquer Heroic content.\n\nWearing Bloodforged Gear in a Heroic Dungeon will apply the Bloody Debuff to you, massively reducing your damage dealt. If you don't have full PvE gear, you can complete High Level Quests, Daily Quests, Normal Dungeons or Flex Raids to continue upgrading your gear.\n\nEquip your PvE gear and defeat the final boss of any Heroic Dungeon!"
DB["Complete any Mythic+ Dungeon"]="Mythic+ Dungeons are timed dungeons of your favorite dungeons, but with a twist.\n\nCreatures, bosses and normal mobs inside of Mythic+ Dungeons can be augmented with an Affix that will try to slow you down.\n\nYou are unable to queue for Mythic+ using the dungeon finder, so we advise you to advocate for members in guild chat or for world chat. Remember to have 1 tank, 1 healer and 3 dps for the Mythic+.\n\nTo begin a Mythic+ the leader of the group must have the rest of the group to travel to that instance (we suggest using a stone of retreat or the first-class-experimental teleporter).\n\nOnce inside, use your Keystone to begin the dungeon!"
DB["Complete any Vertical Ascent scenario by finishing in first place."]="Terminez n'importe quel scénario d'ascension verticale en terminant à la première place."
DB["Complete any Wargame."]="Wargames are a feature on Ascension that allows you to Queue up any Battleground or Arena with the cost of having no queue timer.\n\nWargames allow you to test out your build for free and play against your friends or foes before taking it into the Rated Arenas or allows your guild to duke it out with your rival guild.\n\nTo queue for a Wargame, locate Teri Glozilk in any Capital City.\n\nFind the friend or foe you wish to play against, select your battleground or arena (we recommend arena for small-scale fights) then begin the fight."
DB["Complete any level 60 Heroic Dungeon"]="Complétez n'importe quel donjon héroïque de niveau 60."
