DB["Discover the location of the Fel Commutation Portal in the basement of the Slaughtered Lamb Inn in Stormwind's Mage District and speak with Belpix."]="Fel Commutation allows you to protect your gear in High-Risk PvP.\n\nFind the Fel Commutation Portal in the basement of the Slaughtered Lamb Inn in Stormwind's Mage District. Interacting with the portal will allow you to protect or remove gear slots from Fel Commutation. If you die in High-Risk PvP, you will instead drop gold instead of your gear!\n\nYou can find your max gold lost on death in your character pane at the bottom right by hitting C.\n\nBelpix is standing near the Fel Commutation Portal, speak with him to learn more."
