DB["Equip every slot with an average item level of 72."]="Équipez chaque emplacement d'un niveau d'objet moyen de 72."
DB["Equip every slot with an average item level of 76."]="Équipez chaque emplacement d'un niveau d'objet moyen de 76."
DB["Equip more powerful gear to reach 40 item level."]="You can generally distinguish the power of gear by its Item Level. Mouse over any peice of gear to see the item level.\n\nYou can view your Average Item Level in your character sheet. This is an approximation of how strong your gear is! Higher level dungeons and higher tier raids drop higher item level gear.\n\nComplete Dungeons and higher level quests to acquire more powerful gear until you reach an Average Item Level of 40. You can gain a large boost to your ilvl by upgrading your lowest ilvl pieces of gear."
