DB["Have 3 Epic Mystic Enchants Active!"]="Open the Enchant Collection tab from a Mystic Altar, select an Epic Enchant from your Enchant Collections and apply it to one of the 3 Epic Active Enchant slots!\r\n\r\nActivating Enchants from your collection requires Mystic Orbs, which can be earned from Daily Quests on the Call Board, Dungeons and Raids, Battlegrounds or defeating enemies in the world!\r\n\r\nYou can have 3 different Epic Enchants active at a time."
