DB["Interact with the Call Board in your Capital City. Ask a Guard for directions!"]="Call Boards are found in all major cities and many neutral cities like Booty Bay and level 20 quest hubs!\n\nThese Boards contain Daily Quests, Path of Ascension Quests, Quests you may have missed when they popped up automatically and timed events.\n\nYou should always check the Call Board at max level to pick up Daily Quests.\n\nIf you ever find yourself unsure which zone to travel to while leveling, you can find quests that will guide your path on the Call Board."
DB["Interact with the Fel Commutation Portal and protect your gear by clicking gear slots, then Commute Slot."]="Interact with the Fel Commutation Portal to open up the Fel Commutation menu.\n\nGear slots that are protected by Fel Commutation are highlighted in green. You can click a slot to add or remove Fel Commutation. You can commute your entire set of gear if you desire.\n\nYou only lose gold for Fel Commutation when dying in High-Risk. You do not lose gold in No-Risk PvP, PvE deaths, Dungeons, Battlegrounds or Arena. You only lose Fel Commutation gold when dying to another player in High-Risk PvP.\n\nOpen the Fel Commutation Portal and protect your gear by clicking unhighlighted slots."
