DB["Load a featured end-game build"]="Max level builds are significantly more powerful than leveling builds. It's vital that you upgrade your build at max level to succeed in end-game content.\n\nYou can find many end-game ready builds in the Hero Architect. Hit N, then click the Hero Architect Tab, then select either Level 60 or 70 Builds depending on your current level.\n\nYou can scroll through high rated end game builds to find one that matches your playstyle! \n\nEnd-game builds rely on Mystic Enchants. Each build will show the required Mystic Enchants at the bottom of the build page. You should acquire the Legendary and Epic enchants suggested immediately to ensure the build works as intended, then seek out the Blue and Green enchants as soon as possible.\n\nIt is highly recommended you try out featured builds before trying to create your own end-game build. You can also reference high rated builds when creating your own to start with a strong foundation.\n\nOnce you choose a build and begin to grow comfortable with it, don't be afraid to experiment and adjust the build to your specific style of play."
