DB["Obtain 1 Bazaar Token"]="Bazaar Tokens are used within Tiraxis' Ethereal Bazaar.\n\nBazaar Tokens can be found from the Auction House and bought in packs or bought from the Donation Store.\n\nThe Ethereal Bazaar allows you to augment your hero with your taste of fashion, with Bazaar Tokens used as the currency to purchase items."
