DB["Obtain an Untarnished Mystic Scroll"]="Mystic Extracts are earned when you successfully raise your Mystic Enchanting level. \n\nYou gain experience towards your Mystic Enchanting level by reforging Mystic Scrolls using a Mystic Altar. Reaching enough experience to reach a new Mystic Enchanting level will grant you one Mystic Extract.\n\nYou can find Mystic Altars by opening the world map and looking for the purple altar icon showing their locations, or ask players outside the Auction House in Orgrimmar or Stormwind to place a Portable Mystic Altar! These are Altars that other players summon and are often found outside the Auction House.\n\nTo otain a Mystic Enchant, right click a Mystic Altar, select Obtain Untarnished Mystic Scroll and then click Obtain to receive your very own Untarnished Mystic Scroll. Then reforge it to turn it into a Mystic Enchant!\n\nUse the Mystic Altar to reforge your Mystic Scrolls by clicking Reforge to roll a new Mystic Enchantment of any rarity until you get one that you like.\n\nKeep obtaining Untarnished Mystic Scrolls and reforging Mystic Scrolls you don't want into Mystic Enchantments until the experience bar fills up and you earn a Mystic Extract!"
