DB["Rank Up your Spells at a Beginner's Book of Ascension."]="New spell ranks will become available to learn as you gain levels. Training your spells to their current max rank is key to surviving on Ascension.\n\nYou can train your spells and abilities up to level 20 at the Beginner's Book of Ascension, found in Starting Zones and in quest hubs level 20 or below.\n\nYou can train your spells past level 20 from any class trainer in major cities, or if you obtain your own Book of Ascension. Many players you find in the world have a portable Book of Ascension as well, so don't hesitate to ask someone to summon one if you need to train new spell ranks! You can keep your eyes out for a portable book by selecting the magnifying lense on the mini-map, and then selecting Class Trainer from the dropdown menu. This will highlight Book of Ascension on the mini map."
