DB["Reach level 15"]="Continue your journey and acquire enough experience to reach level 15. \n\nAs you continue advancing in levels you will have to travel to new zones to find quests and creatures closer to your level to continue gaining experience.\n\nHit M, then right click the map. This will zoom you out to the overall World Map. Mouseover the areas around your current zone. You will see the zone's level range in the top center of the map.\n\nFind the nearby zone that is level 10+ and travel there to discover new quests and continue your journey to level 15."
DB["Reach level 20"]="Continue your journey and acquire enough experience to reach level 20. \n\nAs you gain levels more difficult quests will become available to you. Many quest givers will display a Grey Exclamation Mark indicating they will offer you a quest when you are higher level.\n\nContinue to accept and complete new quests, venturing into more difficult areas as you gain experience until you reach level 20!"
