DB["Reach level 70"]="Continue your journey in Outlands and acquire enough experience to reach level 70. \n\nAs you continue advancing in levels you will have to travel to new zones to find quests and creatures closer to your level to continue gaining experience.\n\nHit M, then right click the map. This will zoom you out to the overall World Map. Mouseover the areas around your current zone. You will see the zone's level range in the top center of the map.\n\nFind a zone that matches your level and travel there to discover new quests and continue your journey to level 70."
