DB["Resurrect in Closest Town or Capital"]="Death isn't the end, and on Ascension you have additional tools to deal with death.\n\nYou will find 2 Spells in the General Tab of your Spell Book that can only be used while you are dead.\n\nResurrect in Capital City will resurrect and teleport you to your faction's closest capital city.\n\nResurrect in Closest Town will teleport you to your faction's closest town. This is usually your current Zone's Quest Hub.\n\nThese spells will allow you to avoid resurrecting in dangerous areas, escape campers in PvP, or just speed up your play session by avoiding a corpse run when you'd rather move on to a new area or quest.\n\nNext time you die, try Resurrecting in Closest Town or Capital City."
