DB["Save 200 Wonkas on Dawnrise Island."]="Sauvez 200 Wonkas sur l'île de Dawnrise."
DB["Save 3 Epic Enchants to your Enchant Collection"]="Extracting a Mystic Enchant will permanently add it to your character's Mystic Enchanting collection, meaning you can use it anytime you want! You should try to extract your favorite Mystic Enchants, especially those that are critical to your build, so you can apply those enchants to one of your 17 Enchantment Slots as you progress.\n\nExtracting a Mystic Enchant will DESTROY the Mystic Scroll.\n\nIf you do not have a Mystic Extract, reforge Mystic Scrolls at the altar until you acquire one.\n\nFind a Mystic Enchant you want to extract into your collection either by reforging Mystic Scrolls, searching the Auction House, or exploring throughout the world!\n\nSelect a Mystic Scroll with an Epic Mystic Enchant you wish to extract while using a Mystic Altar, then click Save to Collection to destroy the scroll and add the Enchant to your collection permanently!\n\nExtract 3 Epic Enchants into your collection."
DB["Save 50 Wonkas on Dawnrise Island."]="Sauvez 50 Wonkas sur l’Île de Dawnrise."
DB["Save 500 Wonkas on Dawnrise Island."]="Sauvez 500 Wonkas sur l'île de Dawnrise."
DB["Save Metzen the Reindeer."]="Sauver Metzen le renne"
DB["Save Mystic Enchants to your Enchanting Collection"]="Extracting a Mystic Enchant will permanently add it to your character's Mystic Enchanting collection, meaning you can use it anytime you want! You should try to extract your favorite Mystic Enchants, especially those that are critical to your build, so you can apply those enchants to one of your 17 Enchantment Slots as you progress.\n\nExtracting a Mystic Enchant will DESTROY the Mystic Scroll.\n\nIf you do not have a Mystic Extract, reforge Mystic Scrolls at the altar until you acquire one.\n\nFind a Mystic Enchant you want to extract into your collection either by reforging Mystic Scrolls, searching the Auction House, or exploring throughout the world!\n\nSelect a Mystic Scroll with a Mystic Enchant you wish to extract while using a Mystic Altar, then click Save to Collection to destroy the scroll and add the Enchant to your collection permanently!\n\nAdd 10 Mystic Enchants to your collection."
DB["Save The Day"]="Sauveur du jour"
DB["Save a Legendary Enchant to your Enchant Collection"]="Extracting a Mystic Enchant will permanently add it to your character's Mystic Enchanting collection, meaning you can use it anytime you want! You should try to extract your favorite Mystic Enchants, especially those that are critical to your build, so you can apply those enchants to one of your 17 Enchantment Slots as you progress.\n\nExtracting a Mystic Enchant will DESTROY the Mystic Scroll.\n\nIf you do not have a Mystic Extract, reforge Mystic Scrolls at the altar until you acquire one.\n\nFind a Mystic Enchant you want to extract into your collection either by reforging Mystic Scrolls, searching the Auction House, or exploring throughout the world!\n\nSelect a Mystic Scroll with a Legendary Mystic Enchant you wish to extract while using a Mystic Altar, then click Save to Collection to destroy the scroll and add the Enchant to your collection permanently!\n\nExtract a Legendary Enchant into your collection."
DB["Save a Mystic Enchant Scroll to your Enchant Collection"]="Extracting a Mystic Enchant will permanently add it to your character's Mystic Enchanting collection, meaning you can use it anytime you want! You should try to extract your favorite Mystic Enchants, especially those that are critical to your build, so you can apply those enchants to one of your 17 Enchantment Slots as you progress.\n\nExtracting a Mystic Enchant will DESTROY the Mystic Scroll.\n\nIf you do not have a Mystic Extract, reforge Mystic Scrolls at the altar until you acquire one.\n\nFind a Mystic Enchant you want to extract into your collection either by reforging Mystic Scrolls, searching the Auction House, or exploring throughout the world!\n\nSelect a Mystic Scroll with an Enchant you wish to extract at a Mystic Altar, then click Save to Collection to destroy the scroll and add the Enchant to your collection permanently!"
