DB["Slay 1 player inside the Blood Bowl."]="The Blood Bowl is a savage event with a PvP Focus. Earn a kill inside the Blood Bowl to gain Bonus Rewards and complete this quest.\n\nThe Blood Bowl will begin at 18:00 and 22:00 Server Time, 5 minutes before it begins, it will announce where it will start in chat, so keep your eyes peeled.\n\nYou do not lose items in the Blood Bowl, but it is recommended to visit there in PvP mode (No - Risk).\n\nOnce there, you will find players fighting a 1v1 death match. If you leave the arena, your rewards will be forfeited and you will have to work your way up to new rewards."
