DB["Transmogrify any item at Marazz or in your Wardrobe"]="Marazz the Transmogrifier will allow you to alter the appearance of your gear and can be found in your Capital City Auction House.\n\nThere is no cost to transmogrify a Vanity quality item! If you wish to transmogrify a non-vanity item you will need to acquire a Rune of Transmogrification from the Auction House.\n\nOnce you apply an appearance to a gear slot, any future gear you equip will also have that appearance! So you can upgrade your gear or change sets without changing your appearance!\n\nTalk to Marazz to bring up the Transmog menu. Select any gear slot you wish to transmogrify. Select the item you wish to apply to that slot, then select Accept from the pop-up menu.\n\nYou can disable Transmogs at Marazz by selecting a slot and clicking Remove transmogs, or you can toggle all transmogs off by selecting the bottom option to \"Toggle Transmog Display.\""
