DB["Use any Titan Scroll."]="Titan Scrolls have the power to Augment every hero in the open world with unique boons to the titan they resemble.\n\nTo obtain a Titan Scroll, simply search on the Auction House: \"Titan Scroll\" and you will be able to purchase one.\n\nTitan Scrolls will announce who refreshed the buff to the Entire World and let them know, who to thank."
