DB["Use the First Class Experimental Teleporter."]="The First Class Experimental Teleporter allows you to get from the Capital City into the World or into other capital cities in a jiffy.\n\nThis Teleporter is located in popular parts of the Capital Cities, it stands out and you won't miss it.\n\nYou will be dropped hundreds of yards into the air, don't worry, we provide a parachute that lasts just long enough to get you to the ground... safely."
